markets.title: Will the Apple Watch be banned?
markets.subtitle: On Jan 31, 2024
markets.rules_primary: If Apple is banned from importing/selling the Apple Watch Series 9 and Ultra 2 on Jan 31, 2024, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The market is not on whether a ban begins on the target date, but on whether it is effective on the target date. Currently (as of January 9, 2024) there is no effective ban because of a court-imposed halt on a ban. If the Apple Watch Series 9 and Ultra 2 are permitted to be imported/sold on the target date of this market, this market will resolve to "no."
